texts.text: >The uphill battle continues, but Period is steadily driven back.
Go!!
*Howl*
Quit pissin' me off!
*Yelp*
We're not finished yet...!
Have another!!
Again and again―
Buzz off!
Please disappear!
A direct attack?! Are you stupid?!
No, we're not.
Gah! From behind?! Shit, I won't make it—
Newbie!
It's over!
Eat this!!
What?!
>[sys user_name] and Shiang Sun's demon allies unleash a joint attack
>and pierce Period's body!
Damn...it...!
D-Did we win...?
AWW YEAAAAAAH!!!
You...got me... Did I...underestimate you humans...?
Yes, you've lost.
Isn't this what you feared most?
That our fellowship would surpass you.
That's why you tried to sever it. Am I wrong?
...I don't recall...admitting defeat...
I may have let my guard down...but I'll never...
Lose to that fellowship...!
Victory...is mine...!
What are you—
What is this?!
>"Launch Code Activated" appears on Shiang Sun's screen.
A missle...is about to launch?!
What did you say?! Wasn't it a bluff?!
It WAS a bluff...but...now that it's come to this...
Everything will be blown to smithereens. A lie...made reality...
Keh-keh-keh. Checkmate...! I win...! I—
Shit, where's the launch point?! —Over the ocean?!
W-W-What's next?! There's nowhere to run...!
...Don't worry, I got this.
>Shiang Sun sits at the computer and types away.
Are you nuts?! It's a military network!
There's no way an amateur hacker can—
That won't be an issue, Vince.
Huh?!
Shiang Sun is no amateur.
He might not look it, but he's the world's greatest hacker.
It's okay, Vince.
What?
Let's believe in our bespectacled Big Bro!
Four-Eyes always delivers in a pinch!
Could you please see beyond my glasses...?
Tch... We're takin' a huge gamble.
Our lives are in your hands, Mr. World's Greatest Hacker.
Hey, I'll repay you with interest.
Gakuto, please count down every five seconds until launch.
You got it.
Even if the hardware is beyond humans, the software shouldn't be.
140 seconds. 135 seconds. 130 seconds.
I knew it. It has its own language, but the base... Is it "that"?
90 seconds. 85 seconds.
"Administrator authentication"? I'm already your administrator.
60 seconds.
One minute left... Wish I'd smoked that cigar...
Vince, hush.
It-It's fine! Everything's fine!
Shoot, I can't get in... What is it? What...am I missing?
....Phew, that was a close one.
>"All Commands Halted" appears on screen.
Thanks for the adrenaline rush, I guess.
You enjoyed that?
I lost 5 kilos in two minutes...
At any rate, you legit hijacked a military network.
Couldn't you control every world government if you felt like it?
I didn't hijack it. There wasn't enough time.
I had my hands full stopping the missile.
So, you could if you had the time?
Hmm... Well, even if I tried, it looks pretty boring...
It's like the Internet without all the fun stuff.
Might as well give it another shot to spice things up!
But first, let's save the Internet.
Ah, right. Everyone, please think up a comment.
>Shiang turns back to the monitor and begins to input code.
Yes, you've lost.
Isn't this what you feared most?
That our fellowship would surpass you.
That's why you tried to sever it. Am I wrong?
What are you—
